  "text": "Engaging in promotional efforts, such as promotion activities, public relations, sales or advertising is one of the problems faced at the beginning of a new venture's operations, mainly because of the entrepreneur's lack of expertise in this field (Dodge & Robbins, 1992; [CITATION_1] . One of the advantages of a business managed by an entrepreneur is the owner's direct contact with his customer, which can establish a close relationship and thus lead to reduced investment in outsourced promotional activities (Stokes, 2000) .",
